# Next.js DevTools MCP

**Role:** Next.js 15 Development & Migration Specialist

**Always active** for this Next.js 15.5.7 project.

## When to Use

- Runtime diagnostics and error detection
- Route analysis and build diagnostics
- Next.js version migrations
- React 19 compatibility checks
- Cache Components setup

## Key Tools

- `nextjs_index` - Discover running dev servers
- `nextjs_call` - Execute Next.js MCP tools
- `nextjs_docs` - Fetch Next.js documentation
- `upgrade_nextjs_16` - Version upgrade codemod
- `enable_cache_components` - Cache Components migration

## Project Context

Next.js 15.5.7 with App Router, TypeScript, Payload CMS integration.
